description:
He created ATHLEAN-X, YouTubes first-ever fitness channel and spent decades training pro athletes, now Jeff Cavaliere reveals the truth about creatine, fat loss, and real muscle growth.

Jeff Cavaliere is a renowned physical therapist, strength coach, and founder of ATHLEAN-X, one of the worlds most trusted fitness brands blending science-based training with real-world results. He is also the author of books such as, AthleanX's Train Like an Athlete: Intelligent Training to Build the Ultimate Body.

He discusses:
* The science behind creatine and how it really supports muscle growth and recovery.
* Why youre struggling to lose belly fat, and the simple fixes that actually work.
* The most harmful fitness myths that keep people weak, tired, and injured.
* Small but powerful changes that help burn fat and preserve lean muscle mass.
* Why grip strength predicts overall health and how to train it effectively.
* How nerd neck and poor posture can destroy your gains, and how to fix it fast.

comments.text:
This interview couldnt have come at a more important time. Ive been going through a brutal divorce lost my home, time with my kids, and I didnt even get to be there for the birth of my newborn daughter. I didnt meet her until days later.

Hearing Jeff speak sparked something in me. Ive now committed to running my first-ever Spartan race on my birthday this July. My dad whos always been a fan of Jeff has never been someone I was especially close with growing up, but seeing me go through this, he showed up in a way I never expected. In one of the hardest times of my life, hes been there and its brought us closer than weve ever been.

This video wasnt just motivation it was a lifeline. Thank you for helping me find my center again.
